text: Susan Blake is an American politician from the state of South Dakota. Blake served in the South Dakota House of Representatives for District 13 from 2009 to 2012. She was the Democratic Party's nominee for Lieutenant Governor of South Dakota in the 2014 gubernatorial election. Blake lives in Sioux Falls, South Dakota. ==References== ==External links== Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Sioux Falls, South Dakota Category:South Dakota Democrats Category:Members of the South Dakota House of Representatives Category:Women state legislators in South Dakota Category:21st-century American politicians Category:21st-century American women politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
